transcript: I built a pool you can dive in without getting wet because this is just an illusion of a fully functioning swimming pool. And even though it looks real, the water is just 2 in deep. The layer of water is suspended above a transparent surface. And on the inside is a massive secret room where it feels like you're underwater. But we didn't build this just for fun. We built this to see if it could hide us from a real assassin. Click here to see if it actually works.
